{"tid":353201,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京近郊一人旅程 求推介","createTime":"2017-08-09T11:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T11:52:59.000Z","uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48c16818215679c637afa56ffc3fee1e6c42a7dc","tid":353201,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"我已經買左9月頭的東京機票 打算自己一個去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次的目標係影靚相 休閒啲 同睇富士山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以行程打算有三日 想去箱根 河口湖 或草津<br />\n未去過近郊 而且搭車會有啲複雜 所以上黎問下各位意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先 三日去箱根 河口湖同埋草津會唔會好趕？<br />\n<br />\n上網睇到有資料建議用 富士箱根三日pass  係咪只係包一次新宿到箱根的來 或 回？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住宿住河口湖定箱根會比較方便？<br />\n<br />\n第一日係咪都係去箱根先會較好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩行程 食野 推薦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求各位推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b54566783893ade260772b0564037ab17306c09","tid":353201,"uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"去鎌倉好過去箱根，不解釋"},{"pid":"17fe1be1cb05a958ac67520d4101b9f560241c53","tid":353201,"uid":130065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"淨係去三日？"},{"pid":"c03265a9b9f57bc71d7940b40a43540ab499e206","tid":353201,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"去草津白根山睇湯釜"},{"pid":"e9096b7abe8d0db508cf3d9f8af34977ebd57e35","tid":353201,